@startuml UC5_CompleteLearningActivity
title UC5 - Complete Learning Activity
!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fredoslav2004/MinimalThemePUML/refs/heads/main/minimal-theme.puml

actor Learner
participant System

Learner -> System: Request current learning activity
System --> Learner: Display question or exercise
loop Until correct answer
    Learner -> System: Submit answer
    System -> System: Evaluate answer
    alt Correct
        System --> Learner: Show success and unlock next step
    else Incorrect
        System --> Learner: Show feedback and prompt retry
    end
end
@enduml
